               <code code="55106-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="OTC - ACTIVE INGREDIENT SECTION"/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>This product is an antibacterial liquid which produces a synergistic effect between the Triclosan is the active ingredient with a volatile carrier such as alcohol.</paragraph>
               </text>
